SUMMARY:Murder Mystery Dinner Theater at Mount Hope Estate
DESCRIPTION:The 18th annual Murder Mystery Dinner Theater at the historic Mount Hope Estate offers an immersive\, interactive culinary “who-done-it.” Running from February 6 through April 26\, 2026\, this thrilling event invites you to step into the role of a detective. \nGuests enjoy a sumptuous four-course meal while interrogating suspicious characters and piecing together clues to solve a captivating crime. Held on Fridays\, Saturdays\, and select Sundays\, it’s the perfect blend of high-stakes drama and fine dining. Can you uncover the truth before the final course is served? \n\nCome Explore Our Lancaster Theaters and the Arts\n\n\nLive Theater\nLive Entertainment\nLive Music\n\n\n\nDinner Theaters\nMurder Mysteries\nThings To Do\n\n\n\nArtisan Collectives\nArt Galleries\nEvents Calendar
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/murder-mystery-at-mount-hope-estate/
LOCATION:Mount Hope Estate & Winery\, 2775 Lebanon Road\, Manheim\, PA\, 17545\, United States
CATEGORIES:Adults Only,Food & Beverage Events,Manheim,Theatrical events
