SUMMARY:Spring Fling Shopping Package at Kitchen Kettle Village
DESCRIPTION:2026 Spring Fling Shopping Package Available to Book Now!\n\n\n\n\nThe Spring Fling Shopping Package begins on March 30th\, 2026\, and is redeemable through June 30th\, 2026.  \nReserve the 2026 Spring Shopping Package for just $40* — a $90 value! \nEnjoy this shopping adventure throughout the Village. Start your journey at Village Handmade to pick up your shopping bag filled with offers and incentives from participating Kitchen Kettle shops\, starting at 9am. \nHere’s what our 2026 package includes: \n• Meal at The Harvest Cafe (up to a $17 value) Open Monday—Saturday\, 8am-5pm\n• Free Travel Beverage Cup from Good Vibes\n• Free Bag of Bruschette Chips from The Olive Basin\n• Free “Please Hold” Adjustable Water Bottle Pouch from Happy Camper\n• Free 15 oz. jar of Kitchen Kettle Queso (your choice) from The Jam & Relish Kitchen\n• Free Shower Burst from The Gift House/Village Soap Co.\n• Free 9-Can Woven Cooler Bag from Aged & Cured\n• Free Tart-Shaped Soy Candle from By Candle Light\n• Free Decorative Tape Measure from Country Life\n• Plus other special offers and incentives \nGrab a friend and treat yourself to a fabulous day of shopping in the Village. Book your package soon and enjoy fun\, food & shopping! \n• $40 per package + tax and booking fee \n• Packages must be booked by May 31st\, 2026\, and redeemed by June 30\, 2026. \nTickets are required for this special event and can be purchased online or by calling 1-800-732-3538 to reserve your spot! Tickets are non-refundable.
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/spring-fling-shopping-package-kitchen-kettle/
LOCATION:Kitchen Kettle Village\, 3529 Old Philadelphia Pike\, (Route 340)\, Intercourse\, PA\, 17534\, United States
CATEGORIES:Children & Family events,Food & Beverage Events,Intercourse, Pennsylvania,Memorial Day Weekend,Shopping
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lancasterpa.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/KKV-Event-Spring-Fling.png
GEO:40.037432;-76.1096271
