SUMMARY:Bird-in-Hand Farmers Market
DESCRIPTION:The Bird-in-Hand Farmers Market is a favorite destination for locals\, as well as out-of-town visitors. It features tons of delicious offerings\, including fresh meats\, cheese and produce\, a wide variety of baked goods\, chocolates and candies\, bulk foods\, spices\, coffee and loose leaf tea\, locally made chips and hard pretzels\, hand-rolled soft pretzels\, fresh-squeezed lemonade\, apple cider\, made-to-order subs\, fried chicken and rows of homemade canned goods. \nCome for a traditional Pennsylvania Dutch style lunch or opt for something more portable\, such as a soft pretzel-wrapped hotdog\, and eat while you stroll the aisles in climate controlled comfort. Looking for a gift or souvenir? The Bird-in-Hand Farmers Market offers many locally made crafts and quilts\, dried and silk flower arrangements\, old fashioned toys\, dolls and doll clothes\, quality leather goods\, t-shirts\, and locally themed souvenirs. \nVisit the Bird-in-Hand Farmers Market for mouth-watering aromas and bountiful displays. Come back for more of the same – time and time again! \n \n\nAdditional Shopping & Fun Things To Do in Lancaster?\n\n\nAmish Products\nConsignment and Thrift Shops\nFarmers Markets\nFurniture\n\n\n\nQuilt Supplies and Fabrics\nGifts & Collectibles\nTheater\, Music\, & the Arts\nKids’ Attractions\nAdults & Couples\n\n\n\nRailroad Attractions\nHistorical & Educational\nZip-Lines\nEvents Calendar
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/bird-in-hand-farmers-market/
LOCATION:Bird-in-Hand Farmers Market\, 2710 Old Philadelphia Pike\, Bird-in-Hand\, PA\, 17505\, United States
