SUMMARY:Lancaster County's Best Kept Secrets Tour - April
DESCRIPTION:Hours\n\nhops will be open Mon thru Sat from 9 to 5 during the tour\nSome businesses will offer additional hours.\n14 businesses will offer Sunday hours. Check each listing for details.\nEateries\, Bakeries & Wineries are not required to hold those hours. Their hours will be posted within your tour ticket\n\nHow Does It Work?\n\nSet up like a home or garden tour\, you’ll travel place to place\, in your own vehicle—going where you want\, when you want.  Your ticket is valid the entire time—do what you can in a day or take  several days – it’s up to you.\nYour ticket is valid April 9 thru 25 and can be used as much as you like\nEach person needs their own ticket to participate!\n\nYou Get\n\nA tour guide booklet describing  the  featured stops\nA map to show you how to easily get around\nValuable Coupons from each business\nGifts\, refreshments\, demos\, or games etc. at each stop\nEntry form to try and win over $1000 in gift cards. (No purchase necessary.  Ask a clerk for a list of rules.)\n\nWhat Will I Find?\n\n\nHome décor & furnishings stores\nCraft shops and artisan wares\nThrift & consignment shops\nFarm Markets\nGreenhouses & nurseries\nA fabulous chocolatier\nA tucked away cannery\nA scenic lavender farm\nClothing & jewelry boutiques\n\n\n\nCreameries and bakeries\nA natural health food store\nVintage & antique shops\nA winery\nLeather crafters and woodworkers\nUnique local eateries and cafes\nA few specialty shops\nAnd so much more!\n\n \n\nUpcoming Dates:\n\nApril 9 – 25\, 2026 – 40+ Featured Stops!\nOctober 8 – 24\, 2026 – 40+ Featured Stops!\nDecember 3 – 12\, 2026 – Twelve Shops of Christmas Shops!\n\n\nAdditional Shopping & Fun Things To Do in Lancaster?\n\n\nAmish Products\nConsignment and Thrift Shops\nFarmers Markets\nFurniture\n\n\n\nQuilt Supplies and Fabrics\nGifts & Collectibles\nTheater\, Music\, & the Arts\nKids’ Attractions\nAdults & Couples\n\n\n\nRailroad Attractions\nHistorical & Educational\nZip-Lines\nEvents Calendar
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/best-kept-secrets-tour-april/
