SUMMARY:Build Your Own Terrarium at That Fish Place
DESCRIPTION:Explore the wonders of Bioactive Terrariums and create your own living ecosystem! \nThis hands-on workshop is perfect for beginners in the terrarium and reptile hobbies! Learn all about setting up and maintaining a bioactive terrarium from an expert with over 20 years of experience! Purchase your ticket today and don’t miss the opportunity to unleash your creativity! \n\nAdditional Shopping & Fun Things To Do in Lancaster?\n\n\nAmish Products\nConsignment and Thrift Shops\nFarmers Markets\nFurniture\n\n\n\nQuilt Supplies and Fabrics\nGifts & Collectibles\nTheater\, Music\, & the Arts\nKids’ Attractions\nAdults & Couples\n\n\n\nRailroad Attractions\nHistorical & Educational\nZip-Lines\n\n\nEvents Calendar
