SUMMARY:Roots Country Market and Auction
DESCRIPTION:Make Root’s Country Market Your Family’s Destination for Food\, Fun\, Handcrafted Items\, and Much More. \nA Variety of Fresh Foods\nFresh-picked\, local produce. Farm-raised meats. Mouthwatering\, homemade baked goods. Prepared foods for any meal. These are just some of the food choices you’ll enjoy when you visit Root’s Country Market. Stock your pantry for the week or meet friends for a hot lunch. The choice is yours—and the options are virtually endless. \nWe are open every Tuesday\, year-round. Our hours are 9 a.m. to 9 p.m. April through October and 9 a.m. to 8 p.m. November through March. \n\nAdditional Shopping & Fun Things To Do in Lancaster?\n\n\nAmish Products\nConsignment and Thrift Shops\nFarmers Markets\nFurniture\n\n\n\nQuilt Supplies and Fabrics\nGifts & Collectibles\nTheater\, Music\, & the Arts\nKids’ Attractions\nAdults & Couples\n\n\n\nRailroad Attractions\nHistorical & Educational\nZip-Lines\nEvents Calendar
