SUMMARY:Green Dragon Farmers Market
DESCRIPTION:Green Dragon Farmer’s Market: A True Lancaster County Experience!\nMillions of shoppers have visited this treasured Lancaster County Amish market since 1932! \nEnjoy a beautiful Friday morning at Lancaster’s favorite local farmer’s market! The Green Dragon Farmers Market & Auction sits humbly on a spacious 60-acre site in the heart of Amish Country. Since its inception in 1932\, we’ve grown to become one of the largest flea markets on the East Coast. \n\nAdditional Shopping & Fun Things To Do in Lancaster?\n\n\nAmish Products\nConsignment and Thrift Shops\nFarmers Markets\nFurniture\n\n\n\nQuilt Supplies and Fabrics\nGifts & Collectibles\nTheater\, Music\, & the Arts\nKids’ Attractions\nAdults & Couples\n\n\n\nRailroad Attractions\nHistorical & Educational\nZip-Lines\nEvents Calendar
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/green-dragon-farmers-market/2026-04-17/
LOCATION:Green Dragon Farmers Market\, 955 North State Street\, Ephrata\, 17522\, United States
CATEGORIES:Ephrata Pennsylvania,Farmers Markets,Food & Beverage Events,Shopping
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lancasterpa.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Green-Dragon-Events.png
