SUMMARY:Schoeneck Mud Sale and Quilt Auction
DESCRIPTION:Items to be sold include: Tools\, household goods\, shrubbery\, horse tack\, quilts\, horses\, sheds and outdoor furniture. \nFood available for purchase. \nStarts at 8:30 am with a Quilt auction starting at 11:00 AM. \n  \nThe Schoeneck Mud Sale and Quilt Auction on the 3rd Saturday of April every year. \n\nMud Sales are a unique Lancaster County tradition to raise funds for local volunteer fire companies. See our complete schedule of Lancaster County mud sales. \nPlease Note: Many of the Fire Companies holding mud sales can always use extra help on the days they receive items and the day of the event.  It takes a LOT of labor to put on a mud sale.
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/schoeneck-mud-sale-and-quilt-auction/2026-04-18/
